{"type":"message","id":"81fb24d6","parentId":"71f0ea35","timestamp":"2026-03-25T00:17:38.989Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"❌ **发现严重安全漏洞！**\n\n**appsettings.json 审查发现：**\n1. ❌ **JWT密钥硬编码在配置文件中**（第8行）- 这是一个严重的安全漏洞！\n   - 密钥直接写在代码库中\n   - 如果代码库泄露，JWT密钥就泄露了\n   - 应该使用环境变量或密钥管理服务\n\n2. ⚠️ JWT密钥长度：68字符，足够长\n3. ⚠️ 监听0.0.0.0:5000（第18行）- 暴露给所有网络接口\n4. ⚠️ 使用HTTP而不是HTTPS（第18行）\n\n现在让我检查其他关键Service文件：","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_fa3c828729ca4eb5b4eb28d3","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/root/.openclaw/tang-sansheng/projects/tianyou-platform/backend/src/Tianyou.Application/Services/FormService.cs"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_003920fa0f694146b5f2f76a","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/root/.openclaw/tang-sansheng/projects/tianyou-platform/backend/src/Tianyou.Application/Services/WorkflowService.cs"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":452,"output":231,"cacheRead":30656,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":31339,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774397851105}}
{"type":"message","id":"561d7f8b","parentId":"81fb24d6","timestamp":"2026-03-25T00:17:39.078Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_fa3c828729ca4eb5b4eb28d3","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"using Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore;\nusing Tianyou.Domain.Entities;\nusing Tianyou.Infrastructure.Data;\nusing System.Text.Json;\n\nnamespace Tianyou.Application.Services;\n\n/// <summary>\n/// 表单管理服务\n/// </summary>\npublic class FormService\n{\n    private readonly TianyouDbContext _context;\n    \n    public FormService(TianyouDbContext context)\n    {\n        _context = context;\n    }\n    \n    /// <summary>\n    /// 创建表单定义\n    /// </summary>\n    public async Task<FormDefinition> CreateFormAsync(string formName, string? description = null, Guid? entityDefinitionId = null)\n    {\n        if (await _context.FormDefinitions.AnyAsync(f => f.FormName == formName))\n        {\n            throw new Exception($\"表单名称 '{formName}' 已存在\");\n        }\n        \n        var form = new FormDefinition\n        {\n            Id = Guid.NewGuid(),\n            FormName = formName,\n            Description = description,\n            EntityDefinitionId = entityDefinitionId,\n            IsPublished = false,\n            CreatedAt = DateTime.UtcNow,\n            UpdatedAt = DateTime.UtcNow\n        };\n        \n        _context.FormDefinitions.Add(form);\n        await _context.SaveChangesAsync();\n        \n        return form;\n    }\n    \n    /// <summary>\n    /// 添加表单字段\n    /// </summary>\n    public async Task<FormField> AddFormFieldAsync(Guid formId, string fieldName, string fieldType, \n        string? label = null, string? placeholder = null, string? defaultValue = null,\n        bool isRequired = false, bool isVisible = true, bool isEditable = true,\n        string? validationRules = null, string? fieldConfig = null)\n    {\n        var form = await _context.FormDefinitions.FindAsync(formId);\n        if (form == null)\n        {\n            throw new Exception(\"表单不存在\");\n        }\n        \n        var field = new FormField\n        {\n            Id = Guid.NewGuid(),\n            FormDefinitionId = formId,\n            FieldName = fieldName,\n            FieldType = fieldType,\n            Label = label ?? fieldName,\n            Placeholder = placeholder,\n            DefaultValue = defaultValue,\n            IsRequired = isRequired,\n            IsVisible = isVisible,\n            IsEditable = isEditable,\n            DisplayOrder = await _context.FormFields.CountAsync(f => f.FormDefinitionId == formId),\n            ValidationRules = validationRules,\n            FieldConfig = fieldConfig,\n            CreatedAt = DateTime.UtcNow\n        };\n        \n        _context.FormFields.Add(field);\n        await _context.SaveChangesAsync();\n        \n        return field;\n    }\n    \n    /// <summary>\n    /// 发布表单\n    /// </summary>\n    public async Task<FormDefinition> PublishFormAsync(Guid formId)\n    {\n        var form = await _context.FormDefinitions\n            .Include(f => f.Fields)\n            .FirstOrDefaultAsync(f => f.Id == formId);\n            \n        if (form == null)\n        {\n            throw new Exception(\"表单不存在\");\n        }\n        \n        if (!form.Fields.Any())\n        {\n            throw new Exception(\"表单至少需要一个字段\");\n        }\n        \n        form.IsPublished = true;\n        form.UpdatedAt = DateTime.UtcNow;\n        \n        await _context.SaveChangesAsync();\n        \n        return form;\n    }\n    \n    /// <summary>\n    /// 获取表单列表\n    /// </summary>\n    public async Task<List<FormDefinition>> GetFormsAsync()\n    {\n        return await _context.FormDefinitions\n            .Include(f => f.Fields)\n            .OrderByDescending(f => f.CreatedAt)\n            .ToListAsync();\n    }\n    \n    /// <summary>\n    /// 获取表单详情\n    /// </summary>\n    public async Task<FormDefinition?> GetFormAsync(Guid formId)\n    {\n        return await _context.FormDefinitions\n            .Include(f => f.Fields.OrderBy(field => field.DisplayOrder))\n            .FirstOrDefaultAsync(f => f.Id == formId);\n    }\n}"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774397859065}}
{"type":"message","id":"0c786ed2","parentId":"561d7f8b","timestamp":"2026-03-25T00:17:39.086Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_003920fa0f694146b5f2f76a","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"using Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore;\nusing Tianyou.Domain.Entities;\nusing Tianyou.Infrastructure.Data;\nusing System.Text.Json;\n\nnamespace Tianyou.Application.Services;\n\n/// <summary>\n/// 工作流服务\n/// </summary>\npublic class WorkflowService\n{\n    private readonly TianyouDbContext _context;\n    \n    public WorkflowService(TianyouDbContext context)\n    {\n        _context = context;\n    }\n    \n    /// <summary>\n    /// 创建工作流定义\n    /// </summary>\n    public async Task<WorkflowDefinition> CreateWorkflowAsync(string workflowName, string? description = null, string? stepsConfig = null)\n    {\n        if (await _context.WorkflowDefinitions.AnyAsync(w => w.WorkflowName == workflowName))\n        {\n            throw new Exception($\"工作流名称 '{workflowName}' 已存在\");\n        }\n        \n        var workflow = new WorkflowDefinition\n        {\n            Id = Guid.NewGuid(),\n            WorkflowName = workflowName,\n            Description = description,\n            StepsConfig = stepsConfig,\n            IsActive = true,\n            CreatedAt = DateTime.UtcNow,\n            UpdatedAt = DateTime.UtcNow\n        };\n        \n        _context.WorkflowDefinitions.Add(workflow);\n        await _context.SaveChangesAsync();\n        \n        return workflow;\n    }\n    \n    /// <summary>\n    /// 启动工作流实例\n    /// </summary>\n    public async Task<WorkflowInstance> StartWorkflowAsync(Guid workflowDefinitionId, Guid? initiatedBy = null, string? instanceData = null)\n    {\n        var workflow = await _context.WorkflowDefinitions.FindAsync(workflowDefinitionId);\n        if (workflow == null)\n        {\n            throw new Exception(\"工作流不存在\");\n        }\n        \n        if (!workflow.IsActive)\n        {\n            throw new Exception(\"工作流未激活\");\n        }\n        \n        var instance = new WorkflowInstance\n        {\n            Id = Guid.NewGuid(),\n            WorkflowDefinitionId = workflowDefinitionId,\n            Status = \"running\",\n            InitiatedBy = initiatedBy,\n            InstanceData = instanceData,\n            StartedAt = DateTime.UtcNow\n        };\n        \n        _context.WorkflowInstances.Add(instance);\n        await _context.SaveChangesAsync();\n        \n        return instance;\n    }\n    \n    /// <summary>\n    /// 创建任务\n    /// </summary>\n    public async Task<WorkflowTask> CreateTaskAsync(Guid instanceId, string taskName, string taskType, Guid? assignedTo = null, string? taskData = null)\n    {\n        var instance = await _context.WorkflowInstances.FindAsync(instanceId);\n        if (instance == null)\n        {\n            throw new Exception(\"工作流实例不存在\");\n        }\n        \n        var task = new WorkflowTask\n        {\n            Id = Guid.NewGuid(),\n            WorkflowInstanceId = instanceId,\n            TaskName = taskName,\n            TaskType = taskType,\n            Status = \"pending\",\n            AssignedTo = assignedTo,\n            TaskData = taskData,\n            CreatedAt = DateTime.UtcNow\n        };\n        \n        _context.WorkflowTasks.Add(task);\n        await _context.SaveChangesAsync();\n        \n        return task;\n    }\n    \n    /// <summary>\n    /// 完成任务\n    /// </summary>\n    public async Task<WorkflowTask> CompleteTaskAsync(Guid taskId)\n    {\n        var task = await _context.WorkflowTasks.FindAsync(taskId);\n        if (task == null)\n        {\n            throw new Exception(\"任务不存在\");\n        }\n        \n        task.Status = \"completed\";\n        task.CompletedAt = DateTime.UtcNow;\n        \n        await _context.SaveChangesAsync();\n        \n        return task;\n    }\n    \n    /// <summary>\n    /// 获取工作流列表\n    /// </summary>\n    public async Task<List<WorkflowDefinition>> GetWorkflowsAsync()\n    {\n        return await _context.WorkflowDefinitions\n            .Where(w => w.IsActive)\n            .OrderByDescending(w => w.CreatedAt)\n            .ToListAsync();\n    }\n    \n    /// <summary>\n    /// 获取工作流详情\n    /// </summary>\n    public async Task<WorkflowDefinition?> GetWorkflowAsync(Guid workflowId)\n    {\n        return await _context.WorkflowDefinitions\n            .FirstOrDefaultAsync(w => w.Id == workflowId);\n    }\n    \n    /// <summary>\n    /// 获取实例详情\n    /// </summary>\n    public async Task<WorkflowInstance?> GetInstanceAsync(Guid instanceId)\n    {\n        return await _context.WorkflowInstances\n            .Include(i => i.Tasks)\n            .Include(i => i.Workflow)\n            .FirstOrDefaultAsync(i => i.Id == instanceId);\n    }\n    \n    /// <summary>\n    /// 获取用户待办任务\n    /// </summary>\n    public async Task<List<WorkflowTask>> GetUserTasksAsync(Guid userId)\n    {\n        return await _context.WorkflowTasks\n            .Include(t => t.Instance)\n                .ThenInclude(i => i.Workflow)\n            .Where(t => t.AssignedTo == userId && t.Status == \"pending\")\n            .OrderByDescending(t => t.CreatedAt)\n            .ToListAsync();\n    }\n}"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774397859080}}
{"type":"message","id":"00ee5266","parentId":"0c786ed2","timestamp":"2026-03-25T00:17:45.935Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"FormService.cs 和 WorkflowService.cs 审查发现：\n\n**FormService.cs:**\n1. ✅ 使用Entity Framework Core（自动防护SQL注入）\n2. ⚠️ 没有XSS防护（validationRules、fieldConfig可能包含恶意脚本）\n3. ⚠️ 没有权限检查\n\n**WorkflowService.cs:**\n1. ✅ 使用Entity Framework Core\n2. ⚠️ 没有XSS防护（stepsConfig、instanceData、taskData可能包含恶意脚本）\n3. ⚠️ 没有权限检查\n\n现在让我检查前端的一些关键页面：","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_41c30fe9b6d440618f09414d","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/root/.openclaw/tang-sansheng/projects/tianyou-platform/frontend/Tianyou.Web/Pages/EntityCreate.razor"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_b47aad5d0e324dd4a4748ef2","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/root/.openclaw/tang-sansheng/projects/tianyou-platform/frontend/Tianyou.Web/Pages/UserManagement.razor"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":2039,"output":207,"cacheRead":31104,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":33350,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774397859087}}
{"type":"message","id":"034bdfe3","parentId":"00ee5266","timestamp":"2026-03-25T00:17:45.971Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_41c30fe9b6d440618f09414d","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"@page \"/entities/create\"\n@using Microsoft.AspNetCore.Authorization\n@attribute [Authorize]\n@inject HttpClient Http\n@inject NavigationManager NavManager\n\n<h3>➕ 创建实体</h3>\n\n<div class=\"row\">\n    <div class=\"col-md-8\">\n        <div class=\"card\">\n            <div class=\"card-body\">\n                <EditForm Model=\"@entityForm\" OnValidSubmit=\"HandleSubmit\">\n                    <DataAnnotationsValidator />\n                    \n                    <div class=\"mb-3\">\n                        <label class=\"form-label\">实体名称 *</label>\n                        <InputText class=\"form-control\" @bind-Value=\"entityForm.EntityName\" placeholder=\"例如：产品\" />\n                        <ValidationMessage For=\"() => entityForm.EntityName\" />\n                    </div>\n                    \n                    <div class=\"mb-3\">\n                        <label class=\"form-label\">表名 *</label>\n                        <InputText class=\"form-control\" @bind-Value=\"entityForm.TableName\" placeholder=\"例如：products\" />\n                        <small class=\"text-muted\">建议使用英文小写+下划线</small>\n                        <ValidationMessage For=\"() => entityForm.TableName\" />\n                    </div>\n                    \n                    <div class=\"mb-3\">\n                        <label class=\"form-label\">描述</label>\n                        <InputTextArea class=\"form-control\" @bind-Value=\"entityForm.Description\" rows=\"3\" />\n                    </div>\n                    \n                    <div class=\"mb-3\">\n                        <button type=\"submit\" class=\"btn btn-primary\" disabled=\"@submitting\">\n                            @if (submitting)\n                            {\n                                <span class=\"spinner-border spinner-border-sm me-2\"></span>\n                            }\n                            保存\n                        </button>\n                        <button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-secondary\" @onclick=\"Cancel\">取消</button>\n                    </div>\n                </EditForm>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</div>\n\n@code {\n    private EntityForm entityForm = new();\n    private bool submitting = false;\n\n    private async Task HandleSubmit()\n    {\n        submitting = true;\n        try\n        {\n            var response = await Http.PostAsJsonAsync(\"api/entities\", entityForm);\n            if (response.IsSuccessStatusCode)\n            {\n                NavManager.NavigateTo(\"/entities\");\n            }\n        }\n        catch (Exception ex)\n        {\n            Console.WriteLine($\"创建失败: {ex.Message}\");\n        }\n        submitting = false;\n    }\n\n    private void Cancel()\n    {\n        NavManager.NavigateTo(\"/entities\");\n    }\n\n    public class EntityForm\n    {\n        public string EntityName { get; set; } = \"\";\n        public string TableName { get; set; } = \"\";\n        public string? Description { get; set; }\n    }\n}"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774397865963}}
{"type":"message","id":"67c8a4ea","parentId":"034bdfe3","timestamp":"2026-03-25T00:17:45.978Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_b47aad5d0e324dd4a4748ef2","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"@page \"/users\"\n@using Microsoft.AspNetCore.Authorization\n@attribute [Authorize]\n@inject HttpClient Http\n@inject NavigationManager NavManager\n\n<h3>👥 用户管理</h3>\n\n<div class=\"mb-3\">\n    <button class=\"btn btn-primary\" @onclick=\"CreateUser\">➕ 新增用户</button>\n    <button class=\"btn btn-secondary\" @onclick=\"LoadUsers\">🔄 刷新</button>\n</div>\n\n@if (loading)\n{\n    <div class=\"text-center\">\n        <div class=\"spinner-border\" role=\"status\">\n            <span class=\"visually-hidden\">加载中...</span>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n}\nelse if (users == null || users.Count == 0)\n{\n    <div class=\"alert alert-info\">暂无用户数据</div>\n}\nelse\n{\n    <div class=\"table-responsive\">\n        <table class=\"table table-striped table-hover\">\n            <thead class=\"table-dark\">\n                <tr>\n                    <th>用户名</th>\n                    <th>邮箱</th>\n                    <th>角色</th>\n                    <th>状态</th>\n                    <th>创建时间</th>\n                    <th>操作</th>\n                </tr>\n            </thead>\n            <tbody>\n                @foreach (var user in users)\n                {\n                    <tr>\n                        <td><strong>@user.Username</strong></td>\n                        <td>@user.Email</td>\n                        <td><span class=\"badge bg-primary\">@user.Role</span></td>\n                        <td>\n                            <span class=\"badge @(user.IsActive ? \"bg-success\" : \"bg-secondary\")\">\n                                @(user.IsActive ? \"激活\" : \"禁用\")\n                            </span>\n                        </td>\n                        <td>@user.CreatedAt.ToString(\"yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm\")</td>\n                        <td>\n                            <button class=\"btn btn-sm btn-warning\" @onclick=\"() => EditUser(user.UserId)\">编辑</button>\n                            <button class=\"btn btn-sm btn-danger\" @onclick=\"() => DeleteUser(user.UserId)\">删除</button>\n                        </td>\n                    </tr>\n                }\n            </tbody>\n        </table>\n    </div>\n}\n\n@code {\n    private List<UserDto> users = new();\n    private bool loading = true;\n\n    protected override async Task OnInitializedAsync()\n    {\n        await LoadUsers();\n    }\n\n    private async Task LoadUsers()\n    {\n        loading = true;\n        try\n        {\n            // 临时模拟数据（实际应调用API）\n            users = new List<UserDto>\n            {\n                new UserDto { UserId = Guid.NewGuid(), Username = \"admin\", Email = \"admin@example.com\", Role = \"管理员\", IsActive = true, CreatedAt = DateTime.Now.AddDays(-30) },\n                new UserDto { UserId = Guid.NewGuid(), Username = \"user1\", Email = \"user1@example.com\", Role = \"普通用户\", IsActive = true, CreatedAt = DateTime.Now.AddDays(-10) }\n            };\n        }\n        catch (Exception ex)\n        {\n            Console.WriteLine($\"加载失败: {ex.Message}\");\n        }\n        loading = false;\n    }\n\n    private void CreateUser()\n    {\n        NavManager.NavigateTo(\"/users/create\");\n    }\n\n    private void EditUser(Guid userId)\n    {\n        NavManager.NavigateTo($\"/users/{userId}/edit\");\n    }\n\n    private async Task DeleteUser(Guid userId)\n    {\n        users.RemoveAll(u => u.UserId == userId);\n        StateHasChanged();\n    }\n\n    public class UserDto\n    {\n        public Guid UserId { get; set; }\n        public string Username { get; set; } = \"\";\n        public string Email { get; set; } = \"\";\n        public string Role { get; set; } = \"\";\n        public bool IsActive { get; set; }\n        public DateTime CreatedAt { get; set; }\n    }\n}\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774397865973}}
{"type":"message","id":"f1534008","parentId":"67c8a4ea","timestamp":"2026-03-25T00:17:53.299Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"前端页面审查发现：\n\n**EntityCreate.razor:**\n1. ✅ 使用Authorize特性保护页面\n2. ✅ 有错误处理（try-catch）\n3. ⚠️ 错误处理只是Console.WriteLine，用户看不到\n4. ⚠️ 没有输入长度验证\n5. ⚠️ 没有XSS防护（虽然Blazor默认转义，但仍需注意）\n\n**UserManagement.razor:**\n1. ✅ 使用Authorize特性\n2. ❌ **使用模拟数据**（第103-106行）- 没有实际调用API！\n3. ⚠️ 删除操作只是从列表中移除，没有实际调用API删除（第126行）\n4. ⚠️ 没有删除确认对话框\n5. ⚠️ 没有权限细分（谁可以删除用户？）\n\n现在让我检查其他几个关键Service和Controller：","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_a0bfd731cd78457888e2d920","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/root/.openclaw/tang-sansheng/projects/tianyou-platform/backend/src/Tianyou.Application/Services/CodeGeneratorService.cs"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_5b7ede2f05584d55964e6b37","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/root/.openclaw/tang-sansheng/projects/tianyou-platform/backend/src/Tianyou.Application/Services/TenantService.cs"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":1645,"output":277,"cacheRead":33088,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":35010,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774397865979}}
{"type":"message","id":"8e0d932c","parentId":"f1534008","timestamp":"2026-03-25T00:17:53.344Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_a0bfd731cd78457888e2d920","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"using Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore;\nusing Tianyou.Domain.Entities;\nusing Tianyou.Infrastructure.Data;\n\nnamespace Tianyou.Application.Services;\n\n/// <summary>\n/// 代码生成服务\n/// </summary>\npublic class CodeGeneratorService\n{\n    private readonly TianyouDbContext _context;\n    \n    public CodeGeneratorService(TianyouDbContext context)\n    {\n        _context = context;\n    }\n    \n    public async Task<string> GenerateEntityCodeAsync(Guid entityId)\n    {\n        var entity = await _context.EntityDefinitions\n            .Include(e => e.Fields)\n            .FirstOrDefaultAsync(e => e.Id == entityId);\n            \n        if (entity == null) throw new Exception(\"实体不存在\");\n        \n        var code = $@\"using System.ComponentModel.DataAnnotations;\n\nnamespace Tianyou.Domain.Entities;\n\n/// <summary>\n/// {entity.EntityName}\n/// </summary>\npublic class {entity.EntityName}\n{{\n\";\n        foreach (var field in entity.Fields)\n        {\n            code += $@\"    [Required{(field.MaxLength.HasValue ? $\"(MaxLength = {field.MaxLength})\" : \"\")}]\n    public {GetCSharpType(field.FieldType)} {field.FieldName} {{ get; set; }}\n\";\n        }\n        \n        code += @\"}\n\";\n        \n        return code;\n    }\n    \n    public async Task<CodeTemplate> CreateTemplateAsync(string templateName, string templateType, \n        string templateContent, string? description = null, string? language = \"csharp\")\n    {\n        var template = new CodeTemplate\n        {\n            Id = Guid.NewGuid(),\n            TemplateName = templateName,\n            TemplateType = templateType,\n            TemplateContent = templateContent,\n            Description = description,\n            Language = language,\n            IsSystem = false,\n            CreatedAt = DateTime.UtcNow,\n            UpdatedAt = DateTime.UtcNow\n        };\n        \n        _context.CodeTemplates.Add(template);\n        await _context.SaveChangesAsync();\n        \n        return template;\n    }\n    \n    public async Task<List<CodeTemplate>> GetTemplatesAsync(string? templateType = null)\n    {\n        var query = _context.CodeTemplates.AsQueryable();\n        \n        if (!string.IsNullOrEmpty(templateType))\n        {\n            query = query.Where(t => t.TemplateType == templateType);\n        }\n        \n        return await query.OrderBy(t => t.TemplateName).ToListAsync();\n    }\n    \n    private string GetCSharpType(string fieldType)\n    {\n        return fieldType.ToLower() switch\n        {\n            \"text\" or \"string\" => \"string\",\n            \"number\" or \"int\" => \"int\",\n            \"decimal\" or \"money\" => \"decimal\",\n            \"bool\" or \"boolean\" => \"bool\",\n            \"date\" or \"datetime\" => \"DateTime\",\n            \"guid\" => \"Guid\",\n            _ => \"string\"\n        };\n    }\n}"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774397873333}}
{"type":"message","id":"07cf313c","parentId":"8e0d932c","timestamp":"2026-03-25T00:17:53.352Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_5b7ede2f05584d55964e6b37","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"using Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore;\nusing Tianyou.Domain.Entities;\nusing Tianyou.Infrastructure.Data;\n\nnamespace Tianyou.Application.Services;\n\n/// <summary>\n/// 租户管理服务\n/// </summary>\npublic class TenantService\n{\n    private readonly TianyouDbContext _context;\n    \n    public TenantService(TianyouDbContext context)\n    {\n        _context = context;\n    }\n    \n    public async Task<Tenant> CreateTenantAsync(string tenantName, string tenantCode, \n        string? domain = null, string? description = null, int maxUsers = 100)\n    {\n        if (await _context.Tenants.AnyAsync(t => t.TenantCode == tenantCode))\n        {\n            throw new Exception($\"租户代码 '{tenantCode}' 已存在\");\n        }\n        \n        var tenant = new Tenant\n        {\n            Id = Guid.NewGuid(),\n            TenantName = tenantName,\n            TenantCode = tenantCode,\n            Domain = domain,\n            Description = description,\n            Status = \"active\",\n            MaxUsers = maxUsers,\n            CreatedAt = DateTime.UtcNow,\n            UpdatedAt = DateTime.UtcNow\n        };\n        \n        _context.Tenants.Add(tenant);\n        await _context.SaveChangesAsync();\n        \n        return tenant;\n    }\n    \n    public async Task<Tenant> UpdateTenantAsync(Guid tenantId, string tenantName, \n        string? description = null, int? maxUsers = null)\n    {\n        var tenant = await _context.Tenants.FindAsync(tenantId);\n        if (tenant == null) throw new Exception(\"租户不存在\");\n        \n        tenant.TenantName = tenantName;\n        tenant.Description = description;\n        if (maxUsers.HasValue) tenant.MaxUsers = maxUsers.Value;\n        tenant.UpdatedAt = DateTime.UtcNow;\n        \n        await _context.SaveChangesAsync();\n        return tenant;\n    }\n    \n    public async Task<Tenant> SuspendTenantAsync(Guid tenantId)\n    {\n        var tenant = await _context.Tenants.FindAsync(tenantId);\n        if (tenant == null) throw new Exception(\"租户不存在\");\n        \n        tenant.Status = \"suspended\";\n        tenant.UpdatedAt = DateTime.UtcNow;\n        await _context.SaveChangesAsync();\n        \n        return tenant;\n    }\n    \n    public async Task<List<Tenant>> GetTenantsAsync()\n    {\n        return await _context.Tenants\n            .Include(t => t.Users)\n            .OrderByDescending(t => t.CreatedAt)\n            .ToListAsync();\n    }\n    \n    public async Task<Tenant?> GetTenantAsync(Guid tenantId)\n    {\n        return await _context.Tenants\n            .Include(t => t.Users)\n            .FirstOrDefaultAsync(t => t.Id == tenantId);\n    }\n}"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774397873346}}
{"type":"message","id":"770d310d","parentId":"07cf313c","timestamp":"2026-03-25T00:17:59.722Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"CodeGeneratorService.cs 和 TenantService.cs 审查发现：\n\n**CodeGeneratorService.cs:**\n1. ✅ 使用Entity Framework Core\n2. ⚠️ 代码生成可能存在注入风险（templateContent没有验证）\n3. ⚠️ 没有权限检查（谁可以生成代码？）\n\n**TenantService.cs:**\n1. ✅ 使用Entity Framework Core\n2. ⚠️ 没有权限检查（谁可以创建租户？）\n3. ⚠️ 没有验证maxUsers范围\n\n现在让我总结所有发现的问题，生成审查报告。让我先检查一下项目文档，看看是否有已知的限制：","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_fd0ef2492ea641d18842125b","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /root/.openclaw/tang-sansheng/projects/tianyou-platform && find . -name \"*.md\" | grep -E \"(README|API|SECURITY)\" | head -10"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_f867268f16f3445cb2fee922","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/root/.openclaw/tang-sansheng/projects/tianyou-platform/README.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":1430,"output":219,"cacheRead":34688,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":36337,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774397873353}}
